Date: Sat, 4 Jul 2026 20:21:44 +0900
Subject: [PATCH 04/14] File_MmtTlv: audio-component metadata + MH-SDT service
 name

MH-audio-component (0x8014): per-track language, description, main-audio
Default, VI ServiceKind. MH-SDT (0x9F): service name + provider, matched to
the program's service_id. MMT SI text is UTF-8.

Signed-off-by: Rainbaby <rainbaby@outlook.jp>
